\begin{block}{Our ``Cool Demo'' Tool}
\begin{itemize}
\item Teaches aspects of our graphics library in bite-sized pieces
\item Automatically generated animation introduces code alongside the output, step-by-step
\item Slider allows students to replay the animation in any order and at any pace
\end{itemize}
\end{block}

