\begin{block}{Conclusions \& Future Work}
Using a modern take on Cognitive Load Theory, we have created an effective and engaging teaching tool.
Further work includes expanding upon the existing demos to cover a larger breadth of information. The library
will be expanded upon to support more and different types of demos. Additionally,
a study should be performed to determine whether this creates a measurable quantitative improvement in
learning.
\end{block}

